        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/52cd1e5b70e7ea798b5a41cd9a51fbef_7496433081687835465.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素战技</color>\n造成2点 <color=#ff9999>火元素伤害</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>此技能结算后：</color> 如果我方手牌中含有 <color=#ffffff>超量装药弹头</color> ，则 <color=#ffffff>舍弃</color> 1张并治疗我方受伤最多的角色1点。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "圆阵掷弹爆轰术",
        "title": "圆阵掷弹爆轰术",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/a36c7a9c9512124baf0b482d8dc69912_3452447836750005441.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素爆发</color>\n造成2点 <color=#ff9999>火元素伤害</color> ，在敌方场上生成 <color=#ffffff>二重毁伤弹</color> 。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "纵阵武力统筹",
        "title": "纵阵武力统筹",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/4b48c030ba601eab2fe4d2375057a617_5992848247016351617.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>被动技能</color>\n【被动】 <color=#ffffff>敌方角色受到超载反应伤害后：</color> 生成手牌 <color=#ffffff>超量装药弹头</color> （每回合1次）"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "超量装药弹头",
        "title": "超量装药弹头",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_6933733400072507195.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>事件牌</color>\n<color=#ffffff>战斗行动：</color> 对敌方「出战角色」造成1点 <color=#ff9999>火元素伤害</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>此牌被舍弃时：</color> 对敌方「出战角色」造成1点 <color=#ff9999>火元素伤害</color> 。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": [],
        "talentImg": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/5dca55a012526872199ffb25f0129241_445786923583409617.png"
      },
      {
        "key": "火元素伤害",
        "title": "火元素伤害",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_2384076818432452515.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "【 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> + <color=#99ffff>冰元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>融化</color> ：本伤害+2\n【 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> + <color=#80c0ff>水元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>蒸发</color> ：本伤害+2\n【 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> + <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>超载</color> ：本伤害+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色\n【 <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> + <color=#99ff88>草元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>燃烧</color> ：本伤害+1，生成回合结束时造成1点火伤害的[ <color=#ffffff>燃烧烈焰</color> ]（可用次数1，最多叠加到2）"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "规则术语",
        "title": "规则术语",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_203491378434643436.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffffff>物理伤害</color>\n物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。\n<color=#ffffff>二重毁伤弹</color>\n<color=#ffd780>出战状态</color>\n<color=#ffffff>所在阵营切换角色后：</color> 对切换到的角色造成1点 <color=#ff9999>火元素伤害</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次数：2</color>\n<color=#ffffff>战斗行动</color>\n我方执行了一次战斗行动后，会轮到对方行动。\n<color=#ffffff>打出具有此规则的手牌是一个战斗行动，而非快速行动。</color>\n<color=#ffffff>舍弃</color>\n通过行动牌或角色技能的效果，将行动牌从手牌或牌库中弃置。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次数</color>\n此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次 <color=#ffffff>可用次数</color> ；\n<color=#ffffff>可用次数</color> 耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      }
